               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; a few lines in the incipit page, alternating with black lines; two initial lines of each section of the text; elements of punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals; some words such as ʾǝňňanǝm (fol. 23vb), kä-zzih bä-ḫwala (fols. 39ra, 71rb), ʾandǝm (e.g., fols. 50rb, 52rb, 53rb), qädamihu qal (fol. 73ra), dagmäňňam (fol. 99rb), sälam (e.g., fols. 162ra, 164rb, 165va), etc.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
